                    <lb n="1"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> rai koṇṭa kōpparakēcaripaṉmakki yā
                    <lb n="2"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> maṉaip poṉṉum taṇṭap poṉṉum ta
                    <lb n="3"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> ṉā<unclear>r va</unclear>cca poṉ muppatu ṉāl paṭṭam mu
